, Англия","England":"Англия","Castle Bromwich, Warwickshire, England":"кастл бромвич, варвиккшир, Англия","lifeSummary":"Alan de Bromwich II родился в 1180 г. в местности бромсгров, варвиккшир, Англия, Великобритания. Его родителей звали Alan de Bromwich I и Madam Bromwich. Он женился на женщине по имени Madam Bromwich около 1215 г. в местности кастл бромвич, варвиккшир, Англия. У них было по крайней мере 2 сына. Он умер около 1250 г. в местности Англия в возрасте 71 год."},"sm":{"1180–about 1250":"1180–e tusa o le 1250","1180–1250":"1180–1250","1185–Female":"1185–Ua Maliu","1225–1287":"1225–1287","–Male":"Ua Maliu","1150–1210":"1150–1210","–Female":"Ua Maliu","about 1250":"e tusa o le 1250","1185":"1185","1250":"1250","1150":"1150","1180":"1180","1215":"1215","1225":"1225","1224":"1224","about 1215":"e tusa o le 1215","1210":"1210","1287":"1287","about 1179":"e tusa o le 1179","about 1210":"e tusa o le 1210","Pedmore, Bromsgrove, Warwickshire, England":"Bromsgrove, Warwickshire, Egelani, United Kingdom","Bromsgrove, Worcestershire, England":"Bromsgrove, Worcestershire, Egelani","England":"Egelani","Castle Bromwich, Warwickshire, England":"Castle Bromwich, Warwickshire, Egelani"},"sk":{"1180–about 1250":"1180–okolo 1250","1180–1250":"1180–1250","1185–Female":"1185–Zosnulá","1225–1287":"1225–1287","–Male":"Zosnulý","1150–1210":"1150–1210","–Female":"Zosnulá","about 1250":"okolo 1250","1185":"1185","1250":"1250","1150":"1150","1180":"1180","1215":"1215","1225":"1225","1224":"1224","about 1215":"okolo 1215","1210":"1210","1287":"1287","about 1179":"okolo 1179","about 1210":"okolo 1210","Pedmore, Bromsgrove, Warwickshire, England":"Bromsgrove, Warwickshire, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Bromsgrove, Worcestershire, England":"Bromsgrove, Worcestershire, England","England":"England","Castle Bromwich, Warwickshire, England":"Castle Bromwich, Warwickshire, England"},"es":{"1180–about 1250":"1180–aproximadamente 1250","1180–1250":"1180–1250","1185–Female":"1185–Fallecida","1